            </p>-->
          </div>
        </div>
        <div xml:id="ppra-l32-Dctctct">
          <head xml:id="ppra-l32-Hctctct">Conclusiones</head>
          <p xml:id="ppra-l32-cdthpd">
            <pc type="pilcrow"/> Prima conclusio lectionis 
            <lb ed="#P" n="8"/>quaedam nomina temporaliter de deo dicuntur
          </p>
          <p xml:id="ppra-l32-aciedh">
            <pc type="pilcrow"/> 2a conclusio deus cepit esse dominus sub tempore 
          </p>
          <p xml:id="ppra-l32-tqddde">
            <pc type="pilcrow"/> 3a conclusio quando aliquid 
            <lb ed="#P" n="9"/>dicitur de deo ex tempore nihil accidit ei <pc type="punctus"/>
          </p>
          <p xml:id="ppra-l32-qqsdda">
            <pc type="pilcrow"/> 4a conclusio cum spiritus sanctus sit donum vel <unclear>da?m</unclear> est a tempore et hoc de lectione praesenti <unclear>via? sancti ele?</unclear>
          </p>
        </div>
